    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-simulation-lab-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are each at required level 1 and are satisfied by standard practice documentation. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in support of a Class II CPB device pre-market submission. The assessment team accepts the simulation evidence as sufficient for the stated decision question.",
